It actually surprised me a bit just how bad the new updated twitter DMs/chat are. Every update makes everything look and feel worse and this is not even limited to twitter, any website that has updated its visual design or user interface has been just a massive quality downgrade.

It's like car dashboards just becoming slightly worse with the years. Useful buttons and knobs get replaced with touchscreen stuff for no real reason except that someone thinks the design must be "improved" and actually functional stuff is not just allowed to exist just as it is.

I actually can't recall a single update that actually made something better or added a useful new feature to any popular website or software in the last decade. At best they just add new stuff in a relatively non-intrusive way that won't interfere with the way you already use it.
